## Configuration

### Propshaft Configuration

```ruby
# config/initializers/assets.rb

# Add additional assets to be compiled
Rails.application.config.assets.paths << Rails.root.join("app", "assets", "videos")

# Precompile additional assets
Rails.application.config.assets.precompile += %w[admin.css admin.js]
```

### Environment-Specific Settings

```ruby
# config/environments/production.rb

Rails.application.configure do
  # Enable asset digesting (fingerprinting)
  config.assets.digest = true
  
  # Use CDN
  config.asset_host = 'https://cdn.example.com'
  
  # Compress CSS
  config.assets.css_compressor = nil  # Propshaft doesn't compress
  
  # Fallback to assets pipeline if a precompiled asset is missed
  config.assets.compile = false
end
```
